<h2 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;">Sign in to Ike</h2>

<p style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#374151;line-height:1.5;">
  Click the link below to sign in to Ike as <strong><%= @email %></strong>. The link expires in 15 minutes and works once.
</p>

<p style="margin:24px 0;">
  <%= link_to "Sign in to Ike", @token_url, style: "display:inline-block;padding:10px 18px;background:#10b981;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;" %>
</p>

<p style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;line-height:1.5;">
  If you didn't request this, you can ignore the email — no one can sign in without clicking the link, and it expires shortly.
</p>

<p style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;line-height:1.5;word-break:break-all;">
  Or copy and paste this URL:<br>
  <%= @token_url %>
</p>
